">here=E2=80=99s a guy</a>:</p>
<blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Steven Ferry carries in his wallet=E2=80=94in =
addition to cash=E2=80=94a supply of small cards created by one of a growin=
g number of pro-cash groups that tout the benefits of physical money. He ha=
nds them to cashiers and leaves them on checks at restaurants.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">=E2=80=9CI paid cash today for a reason :-)=E2=
=80=9D the cards read in part. =E2=80=9CUsing cash can be inconvenient=E2=
=80=A6but what if it=E2=80=99s worth it?=E2=80=9D</p>
